    dc:creator "Huber, John T." ;
    dc:date "2011" ;
    dc:title "The generic placement and identity of Ichneumon punctum Shaw (Hymenoptera, Mymaridae), and designation of a neotype" ;
    fabio:hasPart <https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11161>, <https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11163>, <https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11162> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11161>
    dc:description "Figures 1 - 5. 1 Ichneumon punctum Shaw, scanned reproduction of Shaw's original figure 2 Camptoptera foersteri Girault, habitus dorsal (air dried specimen from High Beech, Epping [Forest], East Sussex, England) 3 Camptoptera foersteri, mesosoma dorsal 4 Ichneumon punctum, neotype, habitus dorsal (critical point dried specimen) 5 Ichneumon punctum, neotype, mesosoma dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11161" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11163>
    dc:description "Figures 9 - 13. Camptoptera foersteri, paratypes; 9 Body, female 10 antenna, male 11 antennal flagellum, female 12 paratype slide (USNM) 13 wings." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11163" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11162>
    dc:description "Figures 6 - 8. Camptoptera saintpierrei Girault, holotype. 6 habitus, dorsal 7 body, dorsal 8 holotype slide (USNM)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11162" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

